{"tid":671522,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"操作疑難： 用 FB 去展示相片","createTime":"2018-05-20T08:07:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T04:17:01.000Z","uid":185452,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2a1f2acbdaf453773c8bcffba02d1478613523a0","tid":671522,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:07:34.000Z","msg":"有野唔識，睇下有冇人解答到。<br />\n<br />\n假設 在自己 FB，開左一個 新 album，叫 &ldquo;ABC&rdquo;，加左啲相片入去。<br />\n<br />\n之後隔一排，想再加相片入去， 假如是 用 PC Desktop 操作嘅話，<br />\n<br />\n我見到 先要 click 入 Album 嘅版面，再 click &ldquo;ABC&rdquo; 選擇 加相。<br />\n但是 這個加相嘅 行動，唔可以為這個 Post 加入 &ldquo;status / description&rdquo;。<br />\n咁在 timeline 顯示，會是加入左 xx 張相片入 ABC，文字會是 Album 原來嘅 description。<br />\n<br />\n但是若果用 手機 app 去做 加相，就唔同。<br />\n可以 寫 post 嘅時候，直接選擇 加去 邊個 Album 。<br />\nTimeline 顯示嘅 會是 新post 嘅 status，加左xx張相片入去 ABC，不會顯示 ABC 嘅 description。<br />\n<br />\n是我 電腦問題？  有冇人有經驗？<br />\n<br />\nsor， 講得 1999。唔明，我嘗試再解釋"},{"pid":"ce7c48c457af005b8a76af471e503b983cbb7e66","tid":671522,"uid":14606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"貼個圖講個分別都懶 邊有人答到你"},{"pid":"3d70d921fee6e312ee172d69046f2ca9b2ee9be6","tid":671522,"uid":185452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce7c48c457af005b8a76af471e503b983cbb7e66","tid":671522,"uid":14606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"貼個圖講個分別都懶 邊有人答到你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:34:07.000Z","msg":"多謝提醒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ee42e914ca1be77b1ddc2f162e96417b9253b1","tid":671522,"uid":185452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"手機版。一打 status，已經可以選擇 加入去 邊個 Album<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rD6JLgo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrD6JLgo.jpg&h=968e0886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\nPC desktop 版。冇得選擇 加去 邊個 Album。 要用我 在第一個貼